    USER[Frontend / Mobile / Partner Apps]

    APIGW[API Gateway]

    AUTH[Supabase Auth / JWT]

    RLS[RLS + RBAC]

    DOMAIN[Domain APIs]

    REALTIME[Realtime Channels]

    WEBHOOK[Webhook Engine]

    EXT[External Consumers]

